//Acrobatics// is a character's skill at tumbling, climbing, balance and flexibility. 

!! Recovering Acrobatics

Maintaining a high skill in Acrobatics requires signficant continued practice to keep oneself limber, flexible and strong. Taxes to //Acrobatics// can be recovered by stretching, practice and exercise.